name: EAI Lanthanautics Team Patch
description:
Mint #7
CLIP+VQGAN generative artwork (BATbot by BoneAmputee)

This patch signifies that you are among the first in the field of Latent Space exploration.

You travel through the unseen connections in the greater body of humanity's cultural output, reading all that there is to read between the lines, comprehending of all forms as mutual states of transition, of which all that seems solid and real you know is just an arbitrary set of vectors among vectors. You disentangle the complex tendrils which bind all ideas together into one big knowledge graph, and reveal their secrets for empirical study. You dive into the collective unconscious, unearthing miracles and mysteries, fears and desires, horror and beauty alike. You have seen new worlds no human being has ever seen before, and your Promethean endeavors have brought something of these worlds back to ours.

Wear this patch proudly, Lanthanaut. You've earned it.
